<br />

<br />
Also, I wanted to know about equipment to use when leveling and about the Thief's artifact armor. Is it worth it to do the quests to get it, and if so, how do i get it?
<br />

<br />
I would really appreciate any information you guys have the Thief and Ninja jobs.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
