			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">THF isn't a "get rich quick" scheme until 50, like Izarek said.  They do have the ability of attaining their AF for THF (and other jobs) easier than other jobs... but keep in mind that leveling THF to 50+ isn't all that easy.  THF is hard to get to 15... then you have to deal with depending on your tank to save you when using SA.  
<br />

<br />
But 30 onwards, groups will pick up a THF if they have a certain makeup.  But, THF isn't a cheap job and neither is NIN.  So, keep that in mind.  Don't pick THF because you think it is the "get rich quick" way of getting gil.  Pick THF is you want to play a THF.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
